A woman who was stabbed 32 times stared down the ex-boyfriend who brutally attacked her in court on Tuesday at his attempted murder trial.

Melissa Dohme's story is a miraculous tale of survival after she lived against the odds, only to fall in love with the paramedic who came to save her following the horrific assault in January 2012.

Miss Dohme, 22, bravely faced Robert Lee Burton Jr in the Florida courtroom, the first time she has seen her ex since he repeatedly knifed her before leaving her to bleed to death on the sidewalk.Â 

